Milburn Stone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milburn_Stone 0 Hugh Milburn Stone (July 5, 1904 – June 12, 1980) was an American actor, best known for his role as "Doc" (Dr. Galen Adams) on the CBS Western series Gunsmoke.
